Introduction

GIDONGDAE (Korean: 기동대; Japanese: ギドンデ) was a five-member boy group under 2Y Entertainment. They released their pre-debut single "Party Like This" on June 3, 2020. On January 12, 2021, Lee Ki Won confirmed that their debut was canceled.
